          <p>We can deliver translations as text files for your design team, or provide complete bilingual layouts in PDF format. For menus and guest directories, we work with RTL Arabic formatting and appropriate typography. Send your InDesign files or finished PDFs—we return print-ready bilingual versions.</p>
        </div>
